{"tid":1026301,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"[求救]有冇地盤巴打有路數介紹？","createTime":"2019-02-18T04:15:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-19T03:50:07.000Z","uid":21530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"e2f279705943802a3e522d8dbf5de0d819ca2b50","tid":1026301,"uid":21530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T04:15:25.000Z","msg":"細路今年21<br />\n上年因為屋企財政問題quit左u<br />\n已經返緊fulltime文職5.5 days 13k<br />\n但因為呢幾個月又有周轉問題<br />\n呢份文職有啲唔夠用<br />\n所以上完堂拎左綠卡諗住返ft地盤搵多啲<br />\n但細路初黎報到<br />\n對返地盤既經驗都只係做過電工𡃁仔(做過機博同會展)<br />\n跟電工師父執工執尾 遞燈jam線鋪線咁<br />\n除左電就可以話係0知識白紙<br />\n之前做𡃁仔個價係750一工<br />\n其實我自己都唔知個價算高定低<br />\n之前係個師父唔夠人fd搭fd咁介紹我去做<br />\n而家就算想搵ft都唔知可以點入手<br />\n希望有呢行既巴絲可以教下路<br />\n就算唔係有工開<br />\n都想知道點去搵工<br />\n肯學肯做唔介意辛苦 好pay就得<br />\n希望大家可以幫下我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n ft/散工我都冇所謂 想真係學到野去做<br />\n預計3月頭開工<br />\n因為而家呢份工要quit都要預早一禮拜通知<br />\n<br />\n希望有巴絲可以幫下手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n麻煩大家 好人有好報<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6b0554a3eba6b92caf04fb36f1543b1024eeca6","tid":1026301,"uid":127864,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T04:47:14.000Z","msg":"我呢邊個價就1000 1工雜工<br />\n但未請人住 係留個價比你睇下"},{"pid":"9d05282070c524f6b57a6a218ed66f310392a873","tid":1026301,"uid":82068,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T04:57:15.000Z","msg":"我呢邊個價就2000 1工雜工<br />\n但未請人住 係留個價比你睇下"},{"pid":"b1616b07640704c91f261cd